<br />

<br />
Ahh but if the code were made to do something like:
<br />

<br />
Attack highest on hate list.
<br />
If above is not in melee range then attack 2nd highest on hate list.
<br />
If above is not in melee range then attack 3rd highest on hate list.
<br />
etc. etc.
<br />

<br />
As I proposed above then you'd still have group friendly root and no way to exploit it. This is how root should work in my mind (why should a monster care if a person is 3 inches closer to him if he hasn't attacked the monster at all? He doesn't when he isn't rooted).
<br />

<br />
It would seriously give us a utility boost in groups that I would love to have.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
