			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Since root keeps a mob in camp when it would normally be doing a death walk, and the tanks have to deal with taking extra damage because of the spell (costing the healers mana as well), I'm thinking that's enough of a penalty. Changing the aggro rules would be a fine change.
<br />

<br />
The other option that might work well would be a toggle switch on the pet window to enable/disable casting. This would let you use the earth pet in a group, and if you saw an add, redirect the pet and turn the spell effect back on. Since we can do this with taunt, it might be nice if we could do it with spell effects as well.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1002541&resize=true" target="_blank" class="postlink">Naladini Dreamfyre</a>
<br />
